How To use:

Unzip it to your desktop or ANYWHERE on your hard drive 
Run urt 4.exe , it will ask you to point to quake. Point it to your ioUrbanTerror.exe file 
Join a server 
Press the "delete" button on your keyboard to bring up the mombot console 
From here you can change the options by typing the command / value 
Example: Join server, press delete, type: "aim 1" without the quotes, and hit enter. you&#039;ve now set auto aim to ON
